<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, user-scalable=yes">
<title>Registro de Visitas · Mi Calendario</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Sora:wght@600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@tabler/icons-webfont@3.30.0/dist/tabler-icons.min.css">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/flatpickr/dist/flatpickr.min.css">
<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/flatpickr"></script>
<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/flatpickr/dist/l10n/es.js"></script>
<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/papaparse@5.4.1/papaparse.min.js"></script>
<style>
*{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}
:root{
  --brand:#185FA5;--brand-l:#eef4fc;--brand-d:#0C447C;
  --ok:#16a34a;--ok-bg:#f0fdf4;--err:#dc2626;--err-bg:#fef2f2;
  --bg:#ffffff;--bg2:#f8fafc;--bg3:#f1f5f9;--bd:#e2e8f0;
  --t1:#0f172a;--t2:#64748b;--t3:#94a3b8;
  --r-md:8px;--r-lg:12px;--r-xl:16px;
  --sh-md:0 4px 6px -1px rgb(0 0 0/.07),0 2px 4px -1px rgb(0 0 0/.04);
  --sh-lg:0 10px 15px -3px rgb(0 0 0/.08),0 4px 6px -2px rgb(0 0 0/.04);
}
body{font-family:system-ui,-apple-system,'Segoe UI',Roboto,sans-serif;background:var(--bg2);min-height:100vh;color:var(--t1);font-size:14px}
.wrap{max-width:560px;margin:0 auto;padding:28px 16px 60px}
.card{background:var(--bg);border:1px solid var(--bd);border-radius:var(--r-xl);box-shadow:var(--sh-lg);padding:28px 24px;position:relative;animation:fadeInUp .35s ease}
@keyframes fadeInUp{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(10px)}to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0)}}

.hd{display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:12px;margin-bottom:20px}
.hd-icon{width:auto;height:auto;background:transparent;color:var(--brand);
  display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:26px;flex-shrink:0}
.hd h1{font-size:19px;font-weight:700;color:var(--t1);letter-spacing:-.2px;line-height:1.25}
.hd p{font-size:12.5px;color:var(--t2);margin-top:3px;line-height:1.4}

.user-banner{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;background:transparent;border-bottom:1px solid var(--bd);padding:0 0 16px;margin-bottom:20px}
.user-avatar{width:44px;height:44px;border-radius:50%;background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--brand),var(--brand-d));
  color:#fff;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:21px;flex-shrink:0;
  box-shadow:0 3px 8px rgba(24,95,165,.35)}
.user-info{flex:1;min-width:0}
.saludo-hola{font-size:15px;font-weight:700;color:var(--t1)}
.saludo-hola .wave{display:inline-block;animation:wave 2s ease-in-out infinite;transform-origin:70% 70%}
@keyframes wave{0%,100%{transform:rotate(0)}15%{transform:rotate(14deg)}30%{transform:rotate(-8deg)}45%{transform:rotate(14deg)}60%{transform:rotate(-4deg)}75%{transform:rotate(10deg)}}
.saludo-mensaje{font-size:12px;color:var(--t2);margin-top:1px}
.change-user{background:#fff;border:1px solid var(--bd);border-radius:50%;width:34px;height:34px;
  display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;color:var(--brand);cursor:pointer;flex-shrink:0;
  font-size:14px;transition:all .15s}
.change-user:hover{background:var(--brand);color:#fff;transform:rotate(180deg)}

.progress-wrap{margin-bottom:20px}
.progress-bar{height:6px;background:var(--bg3);border-radius:10px;overflow:hidden}
.progress-fill{height:100%;background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--brand),var(--brand-d));border-radius:10px;width:0%;transition:width .4s ease,background .3s ease}
.progress-label{font-size:11px;color:var(--t3);margin-top:5px;text-align:right;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.2px}

label{display:block;font-size:12.5px;font-weight:600;color:var(--t2);margin-bottom:6px}
.req{color:var(--err)}
.fg{margin-bottom:16px;position:relative}
input[type=text],input[type=search],select{
  width:100%;padding:10px 12px;border:1.5px solid var(--bd);border-radius:var(--r-md);
  font-size:14px;color:var(--t1);background:var(--bg);transition:border-color .15s;font-family:inherit
}
input:focus,select:focus{outline:none;border-color:var(--brand)}
input.err-field,select.err-field{border-color:var(--err)}
select:disabled,input:disabled{background:var(--bg3);color:var(--t3);cursor:not-allowed;opacity:.7}
.err-msg{font-size:11.5px;color:var(--err);margin-top:4px;display:none}
.err-msg.show{display:block}
.grid2{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:12px}

.of-results{position:absolute;top:100%;left:0;right:0;background:var(--bg);border:1px solid var(--bd);
  border-radius:var(--r-md);box-shadow:var(--sh-md);max-height:260px;overflow-y:auto;z-index:20;margin-top:4px;display:none}
.of-results.show{display:block;animation:dropIn .18s ease}
@keyframes dropIn{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(-4px)}to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0)}}
.of-count{padding:8px 12px;font-size:10.5px;font-weight:700;color:var(--t3);text-transform:uppercase;
  letter-spacing:.4px;background:var(--bg2);border-bottom:1px solid var(--bd);position:sticky;top:0}
.of-opt{padding:10px 12px;cursor:pointer;border-bottom:1px solid var(--bg3);transition:background .1s}
.of-opt:last-child{border-bottom:none}
.of-opt:hover,.of-opt.active{background:var(--brand-l)}
.of-opt-name{font-weight:600;font-size:13px;color:var(--t1)}
.of-opt-meta{font-size:11.5px;color:var(--t2);margin-top:1px}

.sel-card{background:transparent;border:1.5px dashed var(--bd);border-radius:var(--r-md);padding:14px;margin-top:8px;
  display:none}
.sel-card.show{display:block;animation:cardIn .3s ease}
@keyframes cardIn{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(-6px)}to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0)}}
.osc-name{font-family:'Sora',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:13.5px;color:var(--brand);display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;flex-wrap:wrap}
.osc-cat{font-size:10.5px;font-weight:700;background:var(--brand-l);color:var(--brand-d);border-radius:5px;padding:2px 7px}
.osc-dir{font-family:'Sora',sans-serif;font-size:11px;color:var(--brand);margin-top:9px;font-weight:600;
  background:transparent;border:1.5px solid var(--brand);border-radius:20px;padding:4px 11px;
  display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:5px;width:fit-content}
.osc-dir i{color:var(--brand);font-size:12px}
.osc-chips{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:6px;margin-top:9px}
.of-chip{font-size:11px;color:var(--t1);background:transparent;border:1px solid var(--bd);border-radius:20px;
  padding:4px 10px;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:4px;font-weight:500}
.of-chip i{font-size:12px;color:var(--brand)}

.btn-mini-red{
  margin-top:10px;padding:2px 0;font-size:11.5px;font-weight:700;border:none;background:none;
  color:var(--err);cursor:pointer;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:4px;width:auto;transition:color .15s
}
.btn-mini-red:hover{color:#b91c1c;text-decoration:underline}
.btn{width:100%;padding:13px;border:none;border-radius:var(--r-md);background:var(--brand);color:#fff;
  font-size:14.5px;font-weight:600;cursor:pointer;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;gap:8px;transition:background .15s,transform .1s}
.btn:hover{background:var(--brand-d)}
.btn:active{transform:scale(.99)}
.btn:disabled{background:var(--t3);cursor:not-allowed}

.toast{position:fixed;top:20px;left:50%;transform:translateX(-50%) translateY(-20px);background:var(--ok);color:#fff;
  padding:12px 20px;border-radius:var(--r-md);font-size:13.5px;font-weight:600;box-shadow:var(--sh-lg);opacity:0;
  transition:all .25s;z-index:100;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;max-width:90%}
.toast.show{opacity:1;transform:translateX(-50%) translateY(0)}
.toast.error{background:var(--err)}
.status-line{text-align:center;font-size:12px;color:var(--t3);margin-top:14px}
.spinner{width:15px;height:15px;border:2px solid rgba(255,255,255,.4);border-top-color:#fff;border-radius:50%;animation:spin .6s linear infinite}
@keyframes spin{to{transform:rotate(360deg)}}
@media(max-width:480px){.grid2{grid-template-columns:1fr}}

.aseg-row{display:flex;gap:10px;margin-top:0}
.aseg-pill{flex:1;padding:11px 12px;border-radius:var(--r-md);border:1.5px solid var(--bd);cursor:pointer;
  text-align:center;font-weight:700;font-size:13.5px;transition:all .15s;color:var(--t2)}
.aseg-pill:hover{border-color:var(--brand);color:var(--brand)}
.aseg-pill.sel-m{background:#eef4fc;border-color:#185FA5;color:#185FA5}
.aseg-pill.sel-c{background:#fef6e7;border-color:#ef9f27;color:#b36d00}
.hidden{display:none}

.stepper{display:flex;align-items:center;border:1.5px solid var(--bd);border-radius:var(--r-md);overflow:hidden;background:var(--bg)}
.stepper:focus-within{border-color:var(--brand)}
.stepper input{border:none;text-align:center;flex:1;padding:10px 4px;min-width:0}
.stepper input:focus{outline:none}
.step-btn{width:38px;height:41px;border:none;background:var(--bg3);color:var(--brand-d);font-size:15px;cursor:pointer;
  display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0;transition:background .15s}
.step-btn:hover{background:var(--brand-l)}
.step-btn:active{background:var(--brand);color:#fff}

.success-overlay{position:fixed;inset:0;background:rgba(15,23,42,.35);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;
  z-index:200;opacity:0;pointer-events:none;transition:opacity .25s}
.success-overlay.show{opacity:1}
.success-check{width:86px;height:86px;background:#fff;border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;
  box-shadow:var(--sh-lg);transform:scale(.6);transition:transform .35s cubic-bezier(.34,1.56,.64,1)}
.success-overlay.show .success-check{transform:scale(1)}
.success-check i{font-size:42px;color:var(--ok)}

/* ========== CALENDARIO MEJORADO ========== */
.btn-calendario{
  margin-top:10px;background:var(--bg);color:var(--brand);border:2px solid var(--brand);
}
.btn-calendario:hover{background:var(--brand-l)}

.cal-dia{
  padding:8px 2px;border-radius:6px;cursor:pointer;transition:all .15s;
  min-height:50px;position:relative;background:var(--bg);border:1.5px solid transparent;
  display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;justify-content:center;gap:2px;
}
.cal-dia:hover{background:var(--brand-l);border-color:var(--brand);transform:scale(1.05)}
.cal-dia.otro-mes{opacity:0.3;cursor:default;background:var(--bg2)}
.cal-dia.otro-mes:hover{transform:none;border-color:transparent;background:var(--bg2)}
.cal-dia.hoy{
  background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--brand-l),#dbeafe);
  border-color:var(--brand);font-weight:700;
  box-shadow:0 0 0 2px rgba(24,95,165,.15);
}
.cal-dia.seleccionado{
  background:var(--brand);color:#fff;border-color:var(--brand-d);
  box-shadow:0 0 0 3px rgba(24,95,165,.3);
  transform:scale(1.08);
}
.cal-dia.seleccionado .dia-num{color:#fff}
.cal-dia.seleccionado .dia-punto{background:#fff}
.cal-dia .dia-num{font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:var(--t1)}
.cal-dia .dia-punto{width:6px;height:6px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--ok);margin-top:2px}
.cal-dia .dia-punto.multiple{width:14px;height:6px;border-radius:10px;background:var(--brand)}
.cal-dia.con-visita{border-color:var(--ok);background:var(--ok-bg)}
.cal-dia.con-visita.hoy{background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--ok-bg),#dcfce7)}

.cal-filtros{display:flex;gap:8px;margin:12px 0;flex-wrap:wrap}
.cal-filtro{
  padding:6px 12px;border-radius:20px;border:1.5px solid var(--bd);background:var(--bg);
  font-size:11px;font-weight:600;color:var(--t2);cursor:pointer;transition:all .15s;
  display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:4px;
}
.cal-filtro:hover{border-color:var(--brand);color:var(--brand)}
.cal-filtro.activo{background:var(--brand);color:#fff;border-color:var(--brand)}
.cal-filtro i{font-size:13px}

.cal-detalle{
  margin-top:16px;border:1.5px solid var(--bd);border-radius:var(--r-lg);
  overflow:hidden;animation:slideDown .3s ease;background:var(--bg);
}
@keyframes slideDown{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(-10px)}to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0)}}
.cal-detalle-header{
  background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--brand),var(--brand-d));color:#fff;
  padding:14px 18px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;
}
.cal-detalle-header h4{font-size:14px;font-weight:700;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px}
.cal-detalle-header h4 i{font-size:18px}
.cal-detalle-header .badge-count{
  background:rgba(255,255,255,.2);padding:3px 10px;border-radius:12px;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;
}
.cal-detalle-lista{max-height:400px;overflow-y:auto}
.detalle-item{
  padding:14px 16px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--bg3);transition:background .15s;
}
.detalle-item:hover{background:var(--bg2)}
.detalle-item:last-child{border-bottom:none}
.detalle-item-top{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;margin-bottom:8px;flex-wrap:wrap}
.detalle-item .ofi{
  font-weight:700;font-size:13.5px;color:var(--t1);flex:1;min-width:150px;
  display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;
}
.detalle-item .ofi i{color:var(--brand);font-size:15px}
.detalle-item .hora{
  font-size:12px;color:var(--brand);font-weight:700;
  background:var(--brand-l);padding:3px 9px;border-radius:10px;
  display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:4px;
}
.detalle-item .hora i{font-size:12px}
.detalle-item .aseg-badge{
  font-size:10px;font-weight:700;padding:3px 9px;border-radius:10px;
  background:var(--brand-l);color:var(--brand-d);
}
.detalle-item-details{
  display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:6px 12px;font-size:11.5px;color:var(--t2);
}
.detalle-item-details .detail-row{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:5px}
.detalle-item-details .detail-row i{font-size:12px;color:var(--brand);flex-shrink:0}
.detalle-item-details .detail-row strong{color:var(--t1);font-weight:600}
.detalle-item-stats{
  display:flex;gap:10px;margin-top:8px;padding-top:8px;border-top:1px dashed var(--bg3);
}
.stat-chip{
  font-size:11px;font-weight:600;color:var(--t2);
  display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:4px;
  background:var(--bg2);padding:3px 8px;border-radius:8px;
}
.stat-chip i{font-size:12px;color:var(--brand)}

.dia-sin-visitas{
  padding:30px 20px;text-align:center;color:var(--t3);font-size:13px;
}
.dia-sin-visitas i{font-size:32px;display:block;margin-bottom:8px;opacity:.5}

.cal-leyenda{
  display:flex;gap:12px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-top:12px;padding-top:12px;
  border-top:1px solid var(--bd);font-size:10.5px;color:var(--t3);
}
.leyenda-item{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:5px}
.leyenda-dot{width:8px;height:8px;border-radius:50%}
.leyenda-dot.hoy-dot{background:var(--brand);border:2px solid var(--brand-d)}
.leyenda-dot.visita-dot{background:var(--ok)}
.leyenda-dot.multi-dot{width:14px;height:8px;border-radius:10px;background:var(--brand)}

.botonera{display:flex;gap:8px;flex-wrap:wrap}
.botonera .btn{width:auto;padding:8px 14px;font-size:13px;flex:1}

.cal-nav{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;margin-bottom:12px}
.cal-nav .btn-nav{
  width:auto;padding:8px 12px;font-size:13px;flex:0;
  background:var(--bg);color:var(--brand);border:1.5px solid var(--brand);
}
.cal-nav .btn-nav:hover{background:var(--brand);color:#fff}
.cal-nav .btn-hoy{
  width:auto;padding:7px 14px;font-size:11px;flex:0;
  background:var(--brand-l);color:var(--brand);border:1.5px solid var(--brand);
  font-weight:700;
}
.cal-nav .btn-hoy:hover{background:var(--brand);color:#fff}
.cal-titulo-wrap{
  flex:1;text-align:center;
}
.cal-titulo-mes{font-weight:700;font-size:16px;color:var(--t1)}
.cal-titulo-count{font-size:11px;color:var(--t2);margin-top:2px}

.flatpickr-day.flatpickr-disabled,.flatpickr-day.flatpickr-disabled:hover{
  color:#c0c5cd!important;background:transparent!important;cursor:not-allowed
}
.confirm-overlay{position:fixed;inset:0;background:rgba(15,23,42,.5);display:flex;align-items:center;
  justify-content:center;z-index:250;opacity:0;pointer-events:none;transition:opacity .2s}
.confirm-overlay.show{opacity:1;pointer-events:all}
.confirm-box{background:#fff;border-radius:var(--r-xl);padding:26px 22px;max-width:340px;width:90%;
  text-align:center;box-shadow:var(--sh-lg);animation:cardIn .25s ease}
.confirm-icon{width:52px;height:52px;border-radius:50%;background:#fef6e7;color:#b36d00;
  display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:26px;margin:0 auto 12px}
.confirm-box h3{font-size:15.5px;color:var(--t1);margin-bottom:8px}
.confirm-box p{font-size:12.5px;color:var(--t2);line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:18px}
.confirm-botones{display:flex;gap:10px}
.confirm-btn-no{background:var(--bg);color:var(--t2);border:1.5px solid var(--bd)}
.confirm-btn-no:hover{background:var(--bg3)}
.confirm-btn-si{background:var(--brand)}

</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="toast" id="toast"></div>
<div class="success-overlay" id="success-overlay"><div class="success-check"><i class="ti ti-check"></i></div></div>

<div class="wrap">
  <div class="card" id="card-login">
    <div class="hd">
      <div class="hd-icon"><i class="ti ti-user-check"></i></div>
      <div>
        <h1>Ingresar</h1>
        <p>Selecciona tu aseguradora y tu nombre para continuar.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="fg">
      <label>Aseguradora <span class="req">*</span></label>
      <div class="aseg-row">
        <div class="aseg-pill" id="pill-m" onclick="pickAseg('Mapfre')">Mapfre</div>
        <div class="aseg-pill" id="pill-c" onclick="pickAseg('Colmena')">Colmena</div>
      </div>
      <div class="err-msg" id="err-aseg">Selecciona una aseguradora</div>
    </div>
    <div class="fg">
      <label>Funcionario <span class="req">*</span></label>
      <select id="l-func">
        <option value="">Selecciona aseguradora primero...</option>
      </select>
      <div class="err-msg" id="err-lfunc">Selecciona tu nombre</div>
    </div>
    <button class="btn" onclick="doLogin()"><i class="ti ti-arrow-right"></i> Ingresar</button>
  </div>

<div class="confirm-overlay" id="confirm-fecha-overlay">
  <div class="confirm-box">
    <div class="confirm-icon"><i class="ti ti-alert-triangle"></i></div>
    <h3>Vas a registrar una fecha pasada</h3>
    <p>La visita quedará como <strong>Realizada</strong> el día <span id="confirm-fecha-texto"></span>. ¿Confirmas que sí se hizo ese día?</p>
    <div class="confirm-botones">
      <button class="btn confirm-btn-no" id="confirm-fecha-no"><i class="ti ti-x"></i> Cancelar</button>
      <button class="btn confirm-btn-si" id="confirm-fecha-si"><i class="ti ti-check"></i> Sí, confirmar</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

  <div class="card hidden" id="card-form">
    <div class="hd">
      <div class="hd-icon"><i class="ti ti-map-pin-check"></i></div>
      <div>
        <h1>Registro de Visita</h1>
        <p>Completa los datos y tu visita quedará registrada al instante.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="user-banner">
      <div class="user-avatar" id="user-avatar"><i class="ti ti-user"></i></div>
      <div class="user-info">
        <div class="saludo-hola">Hola <span id="saludo-nombre">—</span> <span class="wave">👋</span></div>
        <div class="saludo-mensaje" id="saludo-mensaje">—</div>
      </div>
      <button class="change-user" onclick="cambiarUsuario()" title="Cambiar usuario"><i class="ti ti-repeat"></i></button>
    </div>

    <div class="progress-wrap">
      <div class="progress-bar"><div class="progress-fill" id="progress-fill"></div></div>
      <div class="progress-label" id="progress-label">0% completado</div>
    </div>

    <div class="fg">
      <label>Buscar oficina <span class="req">*</span></label>
      <input type="text" id="of-search" placeholder="Selecciona regional y zonal primero..." autocomplete="off" disabled>
      <div class="of-results" id="of-results"></div>
      <div class="err-msg" id="err-oficina">Selecciona una oficina de la lista</div>
      <div class="sel-card" id="sel-card"></div>
